egion size and show that they satisfy the property of\nequipartition, that is the leading contribution to the symmetry resolved\nentanglement is independent of the symmetry sector.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 May 2021 17:07:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Jun 2021 14:06:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 15 Nov 2021 15:05:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-24"}
