ons in the\ninner 30-kpc region. We discuss new diagnostics to decompose annular power\nspectra to constrain past episodes of jet activity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 May 2021 18:37:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-01"}
